io.github.msdk.spectra.peakinvestigator

Class PeakInvestigatorMsSpectrum

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.msdk.spectra.peakinvestigator.PeakInvestigatorMsSpectrum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MsSpectrum

    public class PeakInvestigatorMsSpectrum
extends Object
implements MsSpectrum
    This class is used provide m/z-dependent mass tolerances from PeakInvestigator by decorating an existing instance of MsSpectrum.
